 blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFor one of you to carry a rope and bring firewood upon his back to sell, by which Allah saves his face, is better for you than asking from people who might give to you or withhold\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25107,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/07\/24\/urwah-no-iman-cannot-trust\/","url_meta":{"origin":15555,"position":4},"title":"Urwah on Trust: No faith for one who cannot be trusted","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Hisham ibn 'Urwah reported: 'Urwah, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cBe not deceived by the prayer of a man, nor by his fasting. Whoever wills can fast and whoever wills can pray, yet there is no religion for one who cannot be trusted.\u201d Source: al-\u012ama\u0304n li Ibn Abi\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42527,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/02\/28\/make-me-partner-with-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":15555,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Shirk: You make me a partner with Allah?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 28, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cWhat Allah wills and what you will.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cHave you made me a partner with Allah? Rather, what Allah wills alone.\u201d Source: al-Adab a